      "content": "ChanMirai C2 went offline during investigation (all ports filtered). The 2001-port pattern (TCP 30000-32000) is a strong Mirai CNC signature. The Felcloud/24 shows high abuse concentration with multiple scanner-tagged IPs. The hosting chain (Felcloud -> Netiface -> DEMENIN) exhibits BPH reseller characteristics with shell company downstream customers. Sample was not retrieved before C2 shutdown.",
